item.title: About
item.description: FortyTwo Eleven is a Swedish-registered company through which koslib & selected partners offer top-class consulting services. Clients are selected very elaborately with focus on cultivating long-term relationships and quality deliverables on a set of niche topics rather than maximizing volume. Focus areas: (tech) AWS (tech) Kubernetes (culture & tech) SRE (culture) DevOps Think we can help? Get in touch at hej@42eleven.com.
